| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2359 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 79820cd3-ac0c-5e9b-966b-4751ce8d1a75"
